{"tid":1490331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以牙還牙，以眼還眼 an eye for an eye, a tooth for a tooth","createTime":"2019-08-20T05:27:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T05:31:52.000Z","uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"145b5dca0b7e4322d0b27c61d1c1504fda13aed5","tid":1490331,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:27:22.000Z","msg":"唔該各位，睇完片睇完新聞唔好得個嬲字，見到施暴者，佢斬你一刀，你斬撚返佢十刀，有多冇少，屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af667f4158ae32f93a56c8272d5a62570a00f7bf","tid":1490331,"uid":237962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:28:26.000Z","msg":"我好喜歡一段說話：<br />\n「當你在凝視深淵時，深淵也在凝視著你」<br />\n人們通常用這番說話制止別人行動升級<br />\n但這些人往往知其一不知其二<br />\n就是凝視著深淵的不是我們<br />\n而是極權者<br />\n我們才是那個深淵<br />\n當被凝視時<br />\n作為深淵<br />\n我們有責任凝視回對方"},{"pid":"85ba6a1734eea11a2da98051594347684c224ba4","tid":1490331,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:28:46.000Z","msg":"屬於香港既#metoo行動上線啦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1490165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1490165</a><br />\n<br />\n用#metto斬返佢十刀<br />\n國際關注！國際關注！"},{"pid":"57b9f00c784885382b773aca0a99989cee6ee04b","tid":1490331,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"當公義不彰，你就係公義嘅執行者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}